      <title>HPS 在 Brookfield 的支持下从 Chorus 收购飞机租赁部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/hps-to-buy-aircraft-leasing-unit-from-chorus-with-brookfield-s-blessing</link>
